    "Content": "```C++\nnamespace add::test\n{\n    /**\n     * My function, add two integer.\n     * @param a arg a, int type\n     * @param b arg b, int type\n     * @return int type, will a + b\n     * @module add.test.add\n     */\n    int add(int a, int b);\n}\n```",
    "ContentSha": "/l7c+f25PcRtwwR3okA0xOhls5bJ9m0Zo288Po4znwQ=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
